title: Piet Mondrian Lozenge Composition with Yellow, Black, Blue, Red and Gray Magnet
description:
Magnet developed from Piet Mondrian’s Lozenge Composition with Yellow, Black, Blue, Red and Gray, 1921, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Add some artistic flare to your magnetic surfaces with this masterpiece from our collection.

  • Single Magnet
  • Dimensions: 2.24 x 2.28 x .25 in.
  • Material: Acrylic
